---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | SATL Lab">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">About</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-neutral-300">
      <p>
        전자공학과 3학년. 회로, 신호, 반도체, 전파를 공부하고
        재현 가능한 형태로 정리합니다.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {["Python", "C++", "Arduino", "LTspice", "MATLAB", "Git"].map((t) => (
          <span class="rounded-full border border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-900 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-300">
            {t}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400">
        GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank">github.com/your-id</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>